{"tid":145444,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"臨急奶佛腳）分享下中文說話嘅野","createTime":"2017-03-06T09:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T08:06:49.000Z","uid":64831,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2df9a9ad16fe76079256e6a7238e6903459db6","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"小弟Pat Pat痕，開左個個說話訓練團，第一二團都差唔多成團，如果未覆你嘅話畀啲時間我搞，先講聲sorry。<br />\n<br />\n開團以外都想分享下考說話嘅經驗，算唔上係咩技巧，亦冇乜特別，其實你可以㩒返上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n可能講下啲基本野，試下解一兩題，有咩想問都可以問我，盡答。<br />\n<br />\n試下解答一啲常見問題：<br />\n<br />\n1. 咩係小組討論？<br />\n唔係辯論，唔係零和遊戲，唔係殺戮<br />\n係show off 自己<br />\n係show off 自己<br />\n係show off 自己<br />\n（就好似幾條友一齊玩逃出遊戲，無限到個逃出人數，你就唔好傻更更咁亂鳩開人拖，梗係第一時間搵出口，畀人開拖就係咁依幾下蜻蜓點水，之後繼續搵出口）<br />\n（開拖唔係唔得，但唔係最終目標）<br />\n（目標同態度好緊要）<br />\n<br />\n2. 同勁人一組點算？<br />\n同勁人一組帶動到個討論氣氛，marker睇得開心，絕對係好事。但好自然會擔心人勁我廢咁點算？其實所謂嘅勁同廢只係睇你講嘅野係有內容定得水份，但我敢講大家讀嘅嘢差唔多，肯讀多少少，識得包裝一下，就已經好過人好多。記住唔好淆，要催眠自己，等自己可以好有自信咁present 出嚟，就算講嘅野再廢，人地聽到起碼覺得舒服。一出聲就疾機，自覺得你冇料到。同勁人一組仲有好處，就係執人口水尾，執住人啲point轉化一下，加啲補充，起碼死唔晒。<br />\n<br />\n3. 同極廢嘅人一組點算？<br />\nShow off 自己<br />\n完"},{"pid":"77a3c902a1f45d9273f39a2f11bf91f1ba380597","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:13:16.000Z","msg":"4. 點show off自己<br />\n首輪發言、中國文化、理論、例子同包裝<br />\n<br />\n（先簡單講下）<br />\n<br />\n首輪發言：好緊要，要畀個好嘅first impression marker。可以做嘅野有好多，可以界題、拋文化理論名言出嚟、為之後嘅發言做鋪設。唔好浪費時間讀題目、歸納人地嘅point。<br />\n<br />\n文化理論名言：上兩年嘅題目已經好清晰咁話你聽，小組討論係玩文化野。如果我係你我襯仲有啲時間就去記下，草下例子名言，而且作文又可以用得返。當然小組討論係不限學科，借用一下通識經野做切入點又得，讀歷史嘅就仲正。當然你同清人講洋炮唔啱嘴形，最上乘就梗係講義和團點樣刀槍不入。但切記文化名言唔好鳩拋出嚟就算，要做拓展要做解說，如果唔係同左膠有咩分別，好似雨傘咁出嚟鳩坐就算？唔好浪費左佢！亦都唔好諗住背左一大堆就臨場亂用，離題一樣GG。"},{"pid":"7f6759eecb6cf7902852547bd35dbbb63e52be70","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:16:09.000Z","msg":"5. 畀人屌打咁點算？<br />\n唔係叫你唔好還拖，舉高手畀人斬。係叫你唔好戀戰，最好就避重就輕。駁到人就梗係駁，駁唔到就擋幾劍之後閃。記住係逃生遊戲唔係殺戮。<br />\n<br />\n點接招？講呢啲：<br />\n「我明白一號同學嘅擔憂，xxxx的確有xxxx嘅不足，但我更加重視嘅係xxxxxx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講自己嘢）」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n****例如：<br />\n<br />\n2014題： 書法 武術 象棋（哪樣最適合中二同學來弘揚文化）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你（象棋）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一號（書法）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我認為象棋有鼓勵競爭的成分，好時候同學對弈係出於對追求嘅勝負，而唔係從中相互欣賞，互相砥礪，而中二同學嘅心智未必足夠成熟，過早灌輪競爭嘅心態唔係咁適當.....'所以我認為書法比象棋更好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我明白一號同學對於象棋可能存在鼓勵競爭嘅擔憂，但我更加著意嘅係象棋所擁有嘅中國文化特質......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講住咁多先"},{"pid":"de3d68ffb484a9fd979a9ea4cc2bb74c0f44105f","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e0b094baad271f0ddacc47923aa9a53cacd05d","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd18dfd7a182231fa8682358bcd5e42f7e96cf7","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b207739dcc2e5a1d7839fe7d75c2d3fd90d1dda","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7419c63f4dea4869a085e1a4d91dd97bc454442a","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3583aaf4469773bbba029d0e1a50b627aafb81","tid":145444,"uid":44593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21256bbfe7cf180a1ff960e7fda581d97d3e57af","tid":145444,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"好實用 即使唔係DSE係出面面試都用得著 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b721ff73a88e5f238a09f69998a703a41126701","tid":145444,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:55:25.000Z","msg":"最尾個擋劍招really helps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申說話得lv2-3"},{"pid":"41107b3ee24da069e77b793162d4d4b714ddefb5","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"晏啲可能搵條題目解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420df5eac1e97083320c0f709fcb97e9bd65a460","tid":145444,"uid":30927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"卷四文化除左五倫仲要準備咩"},{"pid":"acf1e43f55ed9a3c637dd48b634cc895956c546d","tid":145444,"uid":76412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"中英oral 5**留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b86062a51bf592669aedaab242248c3e1a9dfe","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卷四文化除左五倫仲要準備咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最基本就儒家（五端五倫+例子）<br />\n再多少少就玩埋道家（自然觀、生死觀、清靜無為）<br />\n至少有個認識（明佢講緊咩同點樣活用）"},{"pid":"3d028830389509c4ba08a706c688f233d0e56469","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中英oral 5**留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 學嘢就唔敢當，一齊交流下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e494997054b35af47e4e4bbe7da4c8ebd77d351","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>卷四文化除左五倫仲要準備咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最基本就儒家（五端五倫+例子）<br />\n再多少少就玩埋道家（自然觀、生死觀、清靜無為）<br />\n至少有個認識（明佢講緊咩同點樣活用）</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n其實唔少通識concept都好好用<br />\n特別咩提出建議方法、可行性之類"},{"pid":"9d87d441c4325f7bf52557fe1a0aa1f71c825864","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"點樣拋書包點樣展析先為之好，我用例子嚟答你：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170226/s00005/1488045763217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170226%2Fs00005%2F1488045763217&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8d1ced94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170226%2Fs00005%2F1488045763217&h=0ec9db94\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170226/s00005/1488045763217</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得篇文好多嘢可以學，或者有時間我再解釋下"},{"pid":"560a3986e4b80110f08920af27315da9f616fe33","tid":145444,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣拋書包點樣展析先為之好，我用例子嚟答你：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170226/s00005/1488045763217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170226%2Fs00005%2F1488045763217&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8d1ced94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170226%2Fs00005%2F1488045763217&h=0ec9db94\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170226/s00005/1488045763217</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得篇文好多嘢可以學，或者有時間我再解釋下</blockquote><br />\n劉保禧正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b0e8a22fd4507e479eb98ba322fa5145c5214c","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e3d54643eb50e3adf6f35895c00fc682d646d0","tid":145444,"uid":53535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:07:06.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申：dse 中文說話5**"},{"pid":"4ce44c4fb5620a23a5fcb0d49cda7f8bb42e867d","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0eddd1022d66cbf6158a790921488bb2144b28d","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ff87f8423574b31b186d9613b7ac4e72940bf3","tid":145444,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下星期二考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8d41d9a5b68881b32c44f3544a000b8d5d7254","tid":145444,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"（一）首輪發言：<br />\n最基本嘅format:  拋書包+講立場+解釋<br />\n<br />\n問：點拋書包？<br />\n答：捉住題目某一兩主要字眼（概念）作詮釋<br />\n<br />\n例如：（概念：焦慮）<br />\n<br />\n焦慮源於現代社會結構充滿不確定性，人與人的連繫浮動，大家都「單打獨鬥」應付生活，如無根浮萍，容易失落生命的意義。過去建立群體生活的教會、家族在現代社會退場，削弱群體的支援網絡，也改變了我們如何定義自己的身分，自身生命的意義。 社會學家鮑曼（Zygmunt Bauman）就以「液態現代性」（Liquid Modernity）形容社會從過往的固態轉為液態的流動特質，加強生命價值同意義嘅不確定意，造成今日我地所面對住嘅憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n（用理論切入，講解概念嘅背景同成因，又有古今之比）"}]}